# MeEdu API Project Overview

This is a Laravel 8 based API for MeEdu, an online education platform. The project uses PHP 7.4+ with MySQL, Redis, and Meilisearch.

## Key Project Files

- [composer.json](mdc:composer.json) - Project dependencies and autoload configuration
- [README.md](mdc:README.md) - Installation and setup instructions
- [artisan](mdc:artisan) - Laravel command-line interface
- [server.php](mdc:server.php) - Development server entry point

## Core Directories

- [app/](mdc:app) - Main application code
- [routes/](mdc:routes) - API route definitions
- [config/](mdc:config) - Configuration files
- [database/](mdc:database) - Migrations, seeders, and factories
- [tests/](mdc:tests) - Test suite
- [addons/](mdc:addons) - Plugin/addon system
- [storage/](mdc:storage) - File storage and logs
- [public/](mdc:public) - Public web assets

## Technology Stack

- **Framework**: Laravel 8
- **PHP Version**: 7.4+
- **Database**: MySQL 5.6+
- **Cache**: Redis 5.0+
- **Search**: Meilisearch 0.24.0
- **Authentication**: JWT (tymon/jwt-auth)
- **Payment**: Laravel Pay (yansongda/laravel-pay)

## Key Features

- Multi-version API support (v1, v2, v3)
- Frontend and Backend API endpoints
- JWT authentication
- File upload with chunking
- Payment integration
- Social login (QQ, etc.)
- SMS and live streaming (Tencent Cloud)
- Image processing
- QR code generation
